    "biography": "<p>Intelligent, human-sized shape-shifters of wicked character and highly magical nature.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Shape stealing:</strong> Can adopt the form of any human-like creature (7&rsquo; tall or less) observed. Then proceed to attack the person mimicked.</li>\n<li><strong>Trickery:</strong> Will attempt to kill a PC, take on their role, then attack the party by surprise (e.g. during a battle).</li>\n<li><strong>Reversion:</strong> If killed, reverts to its original form.</li>\n<li><strong>Spell immunity:</strong> Unaffected by sleep and charm spells.</li>\n</ul>"
